title: Print, "Title Page, in Livre Nouveau de Morceaux de Fantaisie (New Book of Works of Fantasy)", 1695–1768
medium: Engraving and etching on laid paper
inscribed: Inscribed, in plate, upper right: No. 22; in cartouche: Livre Nouveau de / Morceaux de fantaisie / a divers usages inventé / par François de Cuvilliés / Conseiller Gentillhomme / de Bouche, et Architecte / de Leurs A. S. E. de Cologne. / C. A. de. Lespilliez. Sc. / Monachij.; lower center: Cum. Privil. S. C. Maj.
dimensions:
Sheet: 38.7 x 27.6 cm (15 1/4 x 10 7/8 in.)

description: Cartouche framed by wings of an eagle and plumes; sun at left, flowers, figure playing horn at right and putto; winged dragon, lion, shells on rocky landscape.
